{"tid":684214,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《死神》真人電影 長澤雅美演一護老母","createTime":"2018-05-30T11:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T21:00:40.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a058169f2841471049d800ee7042b178ef365f90","tid":684214,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"根據久保帶人創作的漫畫『死神』改編的真人電影追加了幾位配角的演員名單，我們熟知長澤雅美、江口洋介、真野惠里菜等都將將加盟這部漫改真人電影。『死神』真人電影將在7月20日在日本上映。長澤雅美將飾演黑崎一護的亡母黑崎真咲，真野惠里菜將出演井上織姫（這乳量夠嘛）江口洋介出演黑崎一心，而茶渡泰虎則有小柳友來出演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/190014_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F190014_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c7b3cd5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9570a67573f26d8e08312acaeb022e7350f644cd","tid":684214,"uid":63588,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:08:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咪撚再拍真人版動畫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6802989a92ba55bb08520a0c88412f756f8752aa","tid":684214,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"茶渡的靈壓...消失了..."},{"pid":"36ce341771e3c23f316d639946cfa6fa2e4c4c8f","tid":684214,"uid":15262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"b665660404960e06e671c71cd8939a832a9a2db3","tid":684214,"uid":129169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"店長咁撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d7737188eb031d4552d849474f70577fe8754b","tid":684214,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf54b2d14fb199ae9bd00284148457f93db5997"